                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You create the effects of a  *rune trap* ritual containing  *fireball* . You can have only one trapped rune from a ring of maniacal devices active at a time, even if you have multiple rings, and the rune disappears if you lose your investiture in the ring.",
